Darren Boyd https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Darren_Boyd 0 Darren John Boyd (born 30 January 1971 in Hastings, Sussex) is an English actor who starred in the Sky 1 series Spy, for which he won a BAFTA award. His work in television and film spans comedy and drama.
